\id 2PE - Borna New Testamnet 
\h 2 P'et'ros 
\toc2 2 P'et'ros 
\toc1 2 P'et'ros Woshts Wosho 
\toc3 2 P'et'. 
\mt1 Wosheetso P'et'ros Gitl Wosho 
\imt1 Kindo 
\ip Woshetso P'et'ros woshts gitlts wosho b́ guut'e k'osh k'osh beyoke fa'a yoots krstiyaniwotsshe. B́ woshotse een keewo kootets daniyirwots gond finonat bodaniyo s'ilitsatse tuut gond ash woti beyo k'efosha. Tuuts kic'wotssh biitso wotitwo Iyesusi bo ááwon bek'tswotsnat b́daniferewre bo waazon shishts ashuwots bobeshits danatse tuutson Ik'onat doonzo Iyesus Krstosko ari dano daatse. Guut'tso bítsnor b́ kitsirwo «Krstos aanar waratse» etiru kooti danoshe, han s'ilitsatse keeweyor «Krstos aanar waaraniyere b́teshiye, Ik'o ash jamo b́morratse bíaanisha bako konwor asho b́ t'afitwk'o b́geerawotsne» etfe. 
\iot Jamon mas'aafan b́detstso 
\io1 Kindo 1:1-2 
\io1 Krstiyani s'eegeyo 1:3-21 
\io1 Kootets danirwots 2:1-22 
\io1 Krstos gitlo aanar b́ woo 3:1-18 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Iyesus Krstossh guutsonat woshef wottso Sim'on P'et'rosoke, Noko Izar Izewernat no ato Iyesus Krstosoke fa'a kááw imnetiyok'o mangts imnetiyo daatstswots itsh,  
\v 2 Ik'onat nodoonz Iyesusi danon s'aatonat jeenon itsh ayowe. 
\s1 Ik'i s'aatonat s'eegetsmanats kup'etwok'o b́ íztsok'o 
\p  
\v 3 B́mangonat b́dowon noon s'eegtso bín nodantsatse tuutson b́ Ik'i angon kashonat Ik'o aroosh geyitu jamo noosh imre.  
\v 4 B́ mangonat b́ dowonn mangts k'awntso detstsonat ayidek't een wotts no jangiru aap'wotsi daatsdek'rone, janigiyets aap'anotsatse tuutson gond tewnatse datsanatse fa'a t'afotse k'ay keer Ik'i doyo kaydek'irwotsi it wotishee.  
\v 5 Manatse tuutson keewanots itsh bodabeetwok'o kup'ore, imnetiyatse doo woto, doo wotaatse dano,  
\v 6 danatse b́took keewdek'o, b́ took kordek'atse k'amoon kup'dek'o, k'amoon kup'dek'ats Ik' aro,  
\v 7 sheeng beeyats eshu eshwi shunewo, eshu eshuwi shuneeyatse shuno dabwere.  
\v 8 Keewanots ayaarr itsh bobere itdetsal nodoonz Iyesus Krstosi danosh woteraw shuu deshawwotsi itwoterawok'o iti kotetúne.  
\v 9 Keewanotsi deshawonmó wokts keewo bek'ofalaw aaw dooge, beshts b́morratsnowere b́s'ayintsok'o batk'rere. 
\p  
\v 10 Eshe ti eshwotso! its'eegeyonat itmarat'etsok'o arikon b́woto kitsosh baltsoniyere iki bogo kup'ore, man itk'aliyal b́ jamon gandeyar dihratste.  
\v 11 Mank'oon dúre dúrik wotts nodoonznat no aton Iyesus Krstos mengstots kindo s'eenon itsh imetwe. 
\p  
\v 12 Keewanotsi danfte wotiyalor, it detsts arikeewon itkúp'yalor hanots jango úni aawo itsh gawiyo fal k'ayaatse.  
\v 13 Dunkaniyok'o wotts tiatsanitse t befetsosh úni aawo itsh gawiyo kááw araatniye taash b́be'eyiri.  
\v 14 No doonz Iyesus Krstos taash b́ kiitstsok'on datsanatse káári k'iron tk'aletwok'o danfee.  
\v 15 And taa t kup'ir kááron itatse tk'aleyakon dab keewanotsi úni aawo gawdek'o it falitwok'owe. 
\s1 Krstos mangi jangosh ááwon bek'tswots bo gawts gawo 
\p  
\v 16 Nodoonz Iyesus Krstos kúp'onat gitlo aanar b́weyi jango itsh nokeewor, notookon, eeno b́woto no ááwon bek'aat gawirwotsi bako ash weri gondon k'aniyets tururi jafro shoydek'atniyaaliye.  
\v 17 «Tmaac' k'eeztso tshunts na'o haniye» etiru k'ááro mangts Ik'oke bísh b́woor, Ik'o nihoke mangonat een woton dek're.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:17-18 \xt Mat. 17:1-5; Mar. 9:2-7; Luk'. 9:28-35\x* S'ayin guro abaatse bínton noteshor darotse waats k'ááran no notokon shishrone. 
\p  
\v 19 Jaman nebiyiwots bo keewtso arik b́ wottsok'oniye noosh bogshdek't bo kitsiri, mansh t'alwi beyoke fa'a c'eshosh sheengshde'er it kotfok'o nebiyiwots keewtsono sheengshde'er koto itn geyiyitwe, manowere it k'alit maargoyo b́ gatsfetsosh, datsgatsi mozofu it nibots b́ be'efetsoniye.  
\v 20 Jamoniyere shino t'iwintso itsh geytwo S'ayin mas'aafotse fa'o kon naari bek'on keewetso konwor b tookon b́ gawirwok'o bitsosh b́ falawok'oniye.\f + \fr 1:20 \ft Asho konwor b́ tookosh b́ gawirwok'on bitsosh falatse etirw k'osh bits bitson Nebiyo konworub́ tookon keewratse etiru biitso imosh falfe. \f* 
\v 21 Kon naari bek'o b́jamon ash shunon waratse, ernmó bek'o shayiron jisheyiru ashuwots Ik'oke dek'tinye bokeewi. 
\c 2  
\s1 Kootets Danirwotsi 
\p  
\v 1 Yoots dúron ash ashuwots dagotse kootets nebíyiwots bo teshtsok'o, it dagotsno shinomaants kootets danirwots beetúne, boowere t'af dowet kooti dano ááshon jamok b́ bad'itwok'owe bo woshiri, boon aaniy kewdek'ts doonzo danatse err káárts t'afo botokats bodoweti.  
\v 2 Mank'oon aywots boko wic'its weeri jafrats sha'itunee, bok'alts k'alatse tuutson ariweerindo b́ c'asheeti,  
\v 3 Kootets daniyirwanots gizosh bo k'awntirwatse tuutson botookon bo tarikiyo keewfetsr iti meetune. Aydúroniyere shintson angsho boosh k'anwtsere, arikon t'afonwere bonee b́ kotiri! 
\p  
\v 4 Melakiwotswor dab morro bofinor Ik'o boosh maac'o b́k'ewerawon t'alu dashan ayiwokts gop'otse tipeyarr angshosh koteyarr boteshtwok'o gahanemits boon juwb́k'ri,  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Aze. 6:1—7:24\x* Mank'o kááw naab́fo Nohi k'osh shawat ashuwotsnton kashit, Ik' Ik'iraw ashuwotsi boteshts datswatse t'afit atso b́ dowiyor maac'o k'ewat manoori datsjamo maarratse,  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Aze. 19:24\x* Dabnworu Ik' Ik'iraw jamwots bí angsho boats b́ ariyetwok'o Sedomnat Gomor kitwots tulo bowotefetsosh mic'r bot'afitwok'o boats bí angshi,  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Aze. 19:1-6\x* K'uurwots bofiniru wic'its finatse tuutson kic'efetst teshtso kááwo Lot'nomó b́ kashiyi,  
\v 8 Kááw ash manwere bo dagotse b́ beyor aaw aawon b́ bek'tsonat b́ shishts nemal keewon b́ kashu b kic'efere b́ teshi.  
\v 9 Eshe jaman hank'o b́ wotiyakon doonzo bín ik'iyon beyiru ashuwotssh fadeyotse b́ oritwok'o, morretswotsno awúk'o b́ seziitwok'onat angshi aawosh aawk'o korde'er b́ ja'ituwok'o danfee etee.  
\v 10 Bítsnor kim wotts bo meets shunok'o sha'irwotsnat Ik' alo gac'irwotsi angshosh korde'er b́ k'aniti. 
\p Kootets danirwanots ááw shúk'etsonat bog noona etirwotsi bo wottsotse darotse alirwotsi bo c'ashor sharaatsne.  
\v 11 Melakiwots boyere kúp'wotsnat angetswotsn bowotiyaloru dab doonzo shinatse boon c'ayr nooni beshoon s'eents s'aamiyo shinomaants boats t'intsratsne.  
\v 12 Kootets danirwanotsmó t'iwnintsosh bofalaaw keewoniye bo c'ashiri, bo kambon detsewoonat úd'ewosh shuwetswotsk'o, azeyon boosh b́ shiyetsok'onat t'iwitsndek' falaaw gizwotskok'one, gizwots bo t'afitwok'o boowere b́ jamone t'afitune.  
\v 13 Weeralo bo fintsotse bo k'awntso dek'etúne, boosh bo gene'o aaw sháánatse máshar weeralo gáálir, weralo gálonowere itnton bomor dáshitk wotts meets finon wic'itsonat jiitsitwotsi wotitune.  
\v 14 Morro finatse bo atso korde'aw gusiyi ááwo detsfne, bodetsts mor fini shunotse awror shashwo keyatsne, bo amantsatse kup'ar ned'eraw ashuwotsiye boant'elciri, gizoshe bok'awntiri. C'ashek ashne.  
\v 15 Bo kááw weero k'azk'rat t'afwtserne, gondo finar daatset gizo shuntso Bi'or naay Bel'am weerindo shoydek't sheelk'rernee.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:15-16 \xt Taaw. 22:4-35\x* Bel'amiyere b́ morratse tuutson fayere, noonkeewo falraw daazu ash noon keew keewon keewat bek'etso geyi fino k'eferaniye. 
\p  
\v 17 Ashaanots aats deshaw aats t'úp'ok'one, egurahon jokeyiru dawnotsk'one, nic' etts t'aluwo bonee b́ kotiri.  
\v 18 Darotse beyiru ashuwots dagotse k'az fart boweyiyako ayo ja'arafa'a ashuwotsi k'awnts deshaw míshí aap'o keewon meets tewnonat gusiyon dáshde aani morro maants bojishti.  
\v 19 «S'ayino keshetute» err itsh bo jangiyiti. Asho b́ da'eyor bín da'atsosh guutso wotaarr b́ kéwetwotse bo botookon morrosh guutsne.  
\v 20 No doonzonat noon kashitso Iyesus Krstosi danon datsatsi kiimotse k'az bo keshiyakon aanar kim mann detseyar bo da'eyal shintsoniye bogo iltso ayideniye gondo boosh b́ wotiti,  
\v 21 kááw weerindo bodaniyakon boosh imets S'ayin tzaziyo shuutso maants bo anoniyere kááwi weerindo dananiyere bo ooro k'anefe b́ teshi boosha.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Ari. 26:11\x* «B́ c'ooshtso móósh kano b́ c'oosho maants aani aanefe.» Mank'owere «Gúritso b́ mashiyakon aanar tok'ots b́ p'úp'refoni» etiru arik wotts jewro boats bodre. 
\c 3  
\s1 Doonzo Iyesus B́weetwok'o Jangiyetso 
\p  
\v 1 T mashotso! itsh t guut'irwan gitl woshoniye, git woshúwotsi itsh t guut' keewanotsi gawde'er kááw asaabiyo it detsetwok'o itn kup'shosh etaatniye.  
\v 2 Hniyere shin S'ayin nebiywots bo keewts keewonat it wosheetsots weeron it datstso no doonz wottsonat noon woriits tzaziyo gaw itdek'etwok'o geefe.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Yhu. 18\x* Jamoniyere shino han t'iwintsde'ere, s'uwaatsi aawwotsitse aatsnifetsr bo gond tewni jafrats sha'it k'aldirwots weetune,  
\v 4 Bowere «Doonzo Iyesus weetwe ett jangiyere eterosha b́ teshi? Beree, abee? Yoots nihwots bo k'irts dúron b́ tuutso jam keewo azeetso b́ teshtsok'one b́ beyiri» bo eteti.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Aze. 7:11\x* Ashaanots ay dúroniyere shino daro Ik' aap'on bí azetsok'o datsunwere bdooze aatsonat aatsatse b́ wottsok'o danfetst danatsone bo eteti.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Aze. 7:11\x* Manoori teshts datsunwere aatson k'oot'eyatniye b́ t'afi.  
\v 7 And beyiru daronat datsonmó Ik' ash woterawwots bo t'afit angshi aawotsi tawosh koteyarniye bo tesheti. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Dub. 90:4\x* T mashotso! itmó doonzokere ik aawo kum aawok'o, kum aawo ik aawok'o b́ wottsok'o ik keewan batk'ayere.  
\v 9 Ik ik ashuwots boosh bí artsok'o doonzo keewt b́ jangits keewo s'eenosh ja'aratse, ernmó jam asho naandrone etosh b́ bodetwok'onat asho konwor b́ t'afawok'o b́ geetsotsne itsh b́ k'amiri. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Mat. 24:43; Luk'. 12:39; 1 Tes. 5:2; Bek'. 16:15\x* Doonzo aawonmó danerawon úmp'etsok'o weetwe, manots aawots darwots k'áári eenon beshitúne, darotsi azeets jamo tawon mic'r t'afitwe. Datsunat biyatse finets keew jamo mis'etwe,\f + \fr 3:10 \ft K'osh bitson datsonat bitsere fa'a jamo sháánats keshetwe eto faletwe. \f* 
\v 11 Eshe jam keewanots hank'on bot'afitkawotiyal, bere, it S'ayin beyon Ik'o arefetsr beyo aawk'oneya itsh geyiyo b́ k'azeti?  
\v 12 Eshe Ik' weet aawo mirac'on kotirwotsnat káári b́ weetwok'o k'alirwotsi wotoore, manoor daro tawon mic'r t'afitwe, azeetswots taw k'ees'on woc'wtsitúne,  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Isa. 65:17; 66:22; Bek'. 21:1\x* Ernmó noosh b́ jangitsok'on kááwo b́ beetwoko handr daronat handr datsatsne no kotiri. 
\p  
\v 14 Mansh t mashotso! jaman b́ wotit aawo kotoka itfa'oni wotiyala, doonzo ik jago it atse gond keewo wee k'efetwo deshawwotsi wotar jeenon iti b́ daatsitwok'o kúp'ar beewere,,  
\v 15 No doonz b́ k'amts k'amo itsh kasho b́ wottsok'o dande'ere, shunetso no eshu P'awlos bísh imets daniteelfok'on itsh b́ guut'tso haniye.  
\v 16 Bí han jangosh b́ wosh jamwotsitsere hank'on guut't, b́ woshwotsitsnoru ik ik keewwots t'iwintsosh falerawwots fa'ane. Dano boosh shaptswotsnat hake baka etiru k'oshwots S'ayin mas'afwotsi bo k'uurirwok'o keewanotsno bo k'uuriri, manowere bo k'alit bo t'afoshe. 
\p  
\v 17 Itmó t mashotso! haniyere shin shino dan itdek'tsotse weeri gondetswots dáróón geetseyar, it need'ts kúp' manatse it dihirawok'o it atso korde'ere,  
\v 18 dab maniyere no doonznat no ato Krstos Iyesus s'aatonat bín danon dambaan dambaan erere, bísh ando dúre dúroshowere mango wotowe! Amen.